quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  40,41,"Ko onon yo yimɓe am, ko waɗi si miɗo nodda on e daɗal, hiɗon nodda lam e Yiite"
  40,42,"Hiɗon nodda lam e yeddugol Allah, sirkana Mo e ko mi alanaa ɗum ganndal, hara non, min miɗo nodda on e Fooluɗo, Suuroowo bakkaatu On"
  40,43,"Sikke alaa, wonnde ko noddoton lam e mun kon, dewal alanaa ɗum aduna, wanaa laakara. E wonnde ruttorde men nden, ko ka Allah, e wonnde ko fantimɓe ɓen, woni Yiite ngen"
  40,44,"Aray nde anndoton, ko mi yewtata on kon; mi fawa fiyaaku am on e Allah. Pellet, Allah ko Reenuɗo jeyaaɓe ɓen"
  40,45,"Allah daɗndi mo, boneeji ɗi ɓe fewjunoo, O fiiltii yimɓe Fir'awna ɓen, ko ɓuri bonnde e lepte"
  40,46,"Yiite ngen, ɓe weeɓitoyte e magge, bimmbi e kiikiiɗe. Ñalnde Darngal daroytoo (wi'oyte): \"Naatee yimɓe Fir'awna ɓen, ka ɓuri saɗtude e lepte"
  40,47,"Janto tuma ɓe yeddondiroyta ka Yiite, lo'unooɓe ɓen wi'ana townitinooɓe ɓen: \"Menen, ko onon men jokkuunoo, taw si on duñanay men geɓal e Yiite ngen"
  40,48,"Townitinooɓe ɓen wi'a: \"En fow, hiɗen e magge. Gomɗii Allah ñaawii hakkunde jeyaaɓe ɓen"
  40,49,"Wonɓe ka Yiite ɓen kadi wi'ana ayninaaɓe Jahannama ɓen: \"Toranee men Joomi mon, O hoynana men, ñalaande (wootere) e lepte ɗen"